name: Succumb to Her Claws
description:
This is Kim, an amazing makeup artist and overall bad ass human I photographed in Germany.  She is a most wonderful combination of beautiful, talented, and SINISTER!!!! Dressed in lace and vinyl, touched by claws, she is a vision of darkness which I cannot resist!


Model and makeup is @justcallmekim_makeup
Belt and collar @tommyvowles
Headdress and Photo Bubbles And Frown
